/** @format */

          <Card sx={{ minWidth: 160 }}>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography
                sx={{ fontSize: 12 }}
                color="text.secondary"
                gutterBottom
              >
                Tasks cleared Last day
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="h3" component="h4">

              </Typography>
            </CardContent>

        <Grid item>

                sx={{ fontSize: 12 }}

                gutterBottom
              >
                Goal Today

              <Typography variant="h3" component="h4">
                0
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item>
          <Card sx={{ minWidth: 160 }}>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography
                sx={{ fontSize: 12 }}
                color="text.secondary"
                gutterBottom
              >
                Personal Best
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="h3" component="h4">
                0
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item>
          <Card sx={{ minWidth: 160 }}>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography
                sx={{ fontSize: 12 }}
                color="text.secondary"
                gutterBottom
              >
                Company Record
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="h3" component="h4">
                0
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Fragment>
  );
};

export default LedgerCards;
